msgstr "Arregla los nombres de clientes"

#: includes/class-aeuw-promo-banner.php:103
msgid ""
"Auto-capitalize names and addresses in WordPress and WooCommerce. Keep "
"invoices and reports professionally formatted."
msgstr ""
"Capitaliza automáticamente nombres y direcciones en WordPress y WooCommerce. "
