msgstr "Limpia el programador de acciones"

#: includes/class-aeuw-promo-banner.php:109
msgid ""
"Remove millions of completed, failed, and old actions from WooCommerce "
"Action Scheduler. Reduce database size instantly."
msgstr ""
"Elimina millones de acciones completadas, fallidas y antiguas del "
