msgstr "Instalar Scheduler Cleaner"

#: includes/class-aeuw-promo-banner.php:114
msgid "Customize your sitemap"
msgstr "Personaliza tu mapa del sitio"

#: includes/class-aeuw-promo-banner.php:115
msgid ""
"Control WordPress native sitemap: exclude post types, taxonomies, specific "
"posts, and authors. No bloat, just options."
msgstr ""
"Controla el mapa del sitio nativo de WordPress: excluye tipos de contenido, "
