msgstr "Instalar Sale Scheduler"

#: includes/class-aeuw-promo-banner.php:156
msgid "Simplify store management"
msgstr "Simplifica la gestión de tu tienda"

#: includes/class-aeuw-promo-banner.php:157
msgid ""
"Clean up WordPress admin for Store Managers. Hide unnecessary menus, keep "
"only orders, products, and customers, plus quick access shortcuts."
msgstr ""
"Optimiza la administración de WordPress para los gestores de tienda. Oculta "
"menús innecesarios, deja solo pedidos, productos y clientes, además de "
"enlaces directos de acceso rápido."

#: includes/class-aeuw-promo-banner.php:158
msgid "Install Easy Store"
msgstr "Instalar Easy Store"

#: includes/class-aeuw-promo-banner.php:162
msgid "Lightbox for Divi"
msgstr "Caja de luz para Divi"

#: includes/class-aeuw-promo-banner.php:163
msgid ""
"Add native lightbox functionality to Divi theme images. No jQuery, fast "
